{"task": "99-bottles", "model": "haiku", "lang": "py", "sample": 0, "solved": true, "turns_used": 1, "out_tok": 128, "cost": 0.000958, "turns": [{"reply": "\n```python\ndef get_bottle_word(n):\n    return \"bottle\" if n == 1 else \"bottles\"\n\ndef print_verse(n):\n    print(f\"{n} {get_bottle_word(n)} of beer on the wall\")\n    print(f\"{n} {get_bottle_word(n)} of beer\")\n    print(\"Take one down, pass it around\")\n    print(f\"{n-1} {get_bottle_word(n-1)} of beer on the wall\")\n\nfor i in range(99, 0, -1):\n    print_verse(i)\n    if i > 1:\n        print()\n```", "usage": {"input_tokens": 163, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 0, "cache_read_input_tokens": 0, "cache_creation": {"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens": 0, "ephemeral_1h_input_tokens": 0}, "output_tokens": 159, "service_tier": "standard", "inference_geo": "not_available"}, "wall_s": 2.8, "exit": 0}]}
{"task": "99-bottles", "model": "haiku", "lang": "py", "sample": 1, "solved": true, "turns_used": 1, "out_tok": 192, "cost": 0.001328, "turns": [{"reply": "\n```python\ndef print_bottles_song():\n    for n in range(99, 0, -1):\n        # First line\n        if n == 1:\n            print(\"1 bottle of beer on the wall\")\n            print(\"1 bottle of beer\")\n        else:\n            print(f\"{n} bottles of beer on the wall\")\n            print(f\"{n} bottles of beer\")\n        \n        # Third line\n        print(\"Take one down, pass it around\")\n        \n        # Fourth line\n        if n - 1 == 1:\n            print(\"1 bottle of beer on the wall\")\n        elif n - 1 == 0:\n            print(\"0 bottles of beer on the wall\")\n        else:\n            print(f\"{n-1} bottles of beer on the wall\")\n        \n        # Blank line between verses (but not after the final verse)\n        if n > 1:\n            print()\n\nprint_bottles_song()\n```", "usage": {"input_tokens": 163, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 0, "cache_read_input_tokens": 0, "cache_creation": {"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens": 0, "ephemeral_1h_input_tokens": 0}, "output_tokens": 233, "service_tier": "standard", "inference_geo": "not_available"}, "wall_s": 3.97, "exit": 0}]}
